<item chapterid="610650" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1956" articlename="妖孽独宠：妃本温柔" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521898094" lastupdate="1521898094" chaptername="第88章我怎么会那么的喜欢你！" chapterorder="92" size="1536" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    抬起眸解释的瞬间，林慕瑶发现席子云俊逸的脸就近在眼前，眉黛如画。

